data.description: Assumable FHA loan available to qualifying buyers at 4.125%! This could make a significant difference in your monthly payment! Plus, this is an amazing price on this home! It feels like you're on vacation when you're in the peaceful backyard! The huge .55-acre lot has plenty of room to play, plus you can enjoy the view and babbling sound of Milton Creek or relax in the steamy hot tub! The detached outbuilding has been nicely finished and includes zonal heat, a kitchenette and bathroom. The one-level home has had many updates: 2019 - new roof, furnace and flooring; 2020 - all new stainless kitchen appliances; 2021 - new electrical panel. The big stuff has all been done! The expansive RV parking area has room for all your toys. If outdoor living is your happy place, then this is the spot for you!
